<p>具体情况具体分析，如果问题本身很简单，自然没必要引入 Docker</p>
<h2 id="compose--脚本">compose + 脚本</h2>
<p>在 <code>docker-compose.yml</code> 文件中定义好外部依赖。然后写一个脚本（bash 或 python 或 &hellip;），按以下步骤执行测试：</p>
<ol>
<li>docker-compose up</li>
<li>数据库初始化（表结构、测试数据）</li>
<li>go test</li>
<li>docker-compose down</li>
</ol>
<p>{% note info %}
整体思路就是这样，比较繁琐，就不演示了
{% endnote %}</p>
<h2 id="dockertest">Dockertest</h2>
<p><a href="https://github.com/ory/dockertest">Dockertest</a> 是一个简易的 Docker 客户端，提供了更便捷的方式管理单元测试的外部依赖。</p>
<h3 id="创建示例项目">创建示例项目</h3>
<p>先安装接下来会用到的依赖：</p>






<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#cdd6f4;background-color:#1e1e2e;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#89dceb">export</span> <span style="color:#f5e0dc">DEMO</span><span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">=</span><span style="color:#f5e0dc">$GOPATH</span>/src/go.chensl.me/dockertest-demo
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>mkdir -p <span style="color:#f5e0dc">$DEMO</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#89dceb">cd</span> <span style="color:#f5e0dc">$DEMO</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>go mod init
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>go get github.com/go-sql-driver/mysql
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>go get github.com/golang-migrate/migrate/v4
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>go get github.com/jmoiron/sqlx
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>go get github.com/ory/dockertest/v3
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>go get github.com/stretchr/testify</span></span></code></pre></div>
