<h3 id="db-方法">DB 方法</h3>
<p>用 <a href="https://github.com/golang-migrate/migrate">golang-migrate</a> 生成 migration 脚本：</p>






<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#cdd6f4;background-color:#1e1e2e;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span>migrate create -ext sql -dir migrations -tz<span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">=</span>Local init</span></span></code></pre></div>






<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#cdd6f4;background-color:#1e1e2e;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cba6f7">CREATE</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">TABLE</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">IF</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">NOT</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">EXISTS</span> <span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">`</span>users<span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">`</span> (
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  <span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">`</span>id<span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">`</span> <span style="color:#89dceb">INT</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">PRIMARY</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">KEY</span> AUTO_INCREMENT,
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  <span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">`</span>name<span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">`</span> <span style="color:#89dceb">VARCHAR</span>(<span style="color:#fab387">255</span>) <span style="color:#cba6f7">UNIQUE</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">NOT</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">NULL</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>);</span></span></code></pre></div>






<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#cdd6f4;background-color:#1e1e2e;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#cba6f7">DROP</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">TABLE</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">IF</span> <span style="color:#cba6f7">EXISTS</span> <span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">`</span>users<span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">`</span>;</span></span></code></pre></div>
